. long. Antenna! segments length (width): I completely covered by eyes; II, 40 (26); III, 80 (20); IV, 63 (23); 
<collectionCode box="[1183,1213,1387,1419]" country="Canada" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13946" name="Royal British Columbia Museum - Herbarium" pageId="4" pageNumber="11" type="Museum">V</collectionCode>
